name: Mio Naruse
description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

link to model used at the bottom.

Naruse Mio from Shinmai Maou no Testament. trained on AnythingV4(V2 trained on NAI)

recommended weights 0.6 - 1.0

recommended tags: red_hair, red_eyes/purple_eyes

V1 copies the art style more and is less compatible while V2 should be more compatible and not copy the artstyle. V2 is also not as accurate with the clothing.

Euler a or DPM++ S2 a Karras usually gives more accurate results

tags for school uniform: skirt, thighhighs, school_uniform

tags for tanktop: (might have to add yellow_shirt as well), yellow_tank_top, denim_shorts, (optional but should help: navel, cleavage)

tags for pajamas: pajamas

tags for hair down (a little tricky to get as most of the training images had her normal hairstyle): Lora at 0.6-0.9, (hair_down:1.3), straight_hair, red_hair, red_eyes/purple_eyes, negative: (two_side_up:1.3), twintails, ribbon, hair_ribbon, black_ribbon, hair_up

model used: "BloodyMight" version of

MightyCorneo (new merges with MeinaHentai) | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

final two images were made by a different version from the same link "BloogyMight-Meina"

modelVersions.name: V2 - trained on more images and more compatible
modelVersions.description:
Some of the prompts were slightly altered from V1 and the vae is probably different along with the model.

can't really do her contract tattoo, probably will make another version with better images and caption for it.

Euler a or DPM++ S2 a Karras usually gives more accurate results
